race.comment: ELITE POWER (3) finished out of the money two starts back then ran fourth in a 1600m contest at Gunnedah two-and-a-half weeks ago after being prominent at the turn. This is a nice drop in grade and well placed here. BROADCAST BOOGIE (7) finished out of the money two starts back then she got a long way back when ninth in a 1600m contest at Dubbo seven weeks ago. Meeting a tougher field but on her best form she is right in contention. PAMPUNI (11) hit the frame two starts ago at Parkes but ran below par last time when sixth over 1600m at Gunnedah. Has the talent to produce a better result. READY FOR LIFT OFF (12) was responsible for a better run last start with a solid fifth over 1400m at Parkes. Well placed and can figure in the finish this time.
